data.description: Perfect rare location with East facing backyard, Single level, truly updated home facing the wide mouth lake with 3 fountains and mountain views, on the longest lake in Arrowhead Lakes, just spectacular!  Too many upgrades to list! New A/C & water heater in 2018, New roof being installed. New dock and pavered landscape in 2023, updated Kitchen and Baths. New windows throughout in 2019 with a new Patio door! Whole house water filtration system in 2020, new view fence. New epoxy garage floor with new a/c split and insulated garage door. Newer Pontoon boat may be purchased on a separate bill of sale for $15,000.00. Bring those buyers who have been waiting for something affordable in prestigious Arrowhead Lakes!
